(1787, 3, '2018-11-03 03:55:09', '2018-11-03 03:55:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gallery blocks have two settings: the number of columns, and whether or not images should be cropped. The default number of columns is three, and the maximum number of columns is eight.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Below is a three column gallery at full width, with cropped images.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery alignfull columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/canola2.jpg\" alt=\"canola\" data-id=\"611\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/canola2/\" class=\"wp-image-611\"/>\n<figcaption>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Donec mollis. Quisque convallis libero in sapien pharetra tincidunt. Aliquam elit ante, malesuada id, tempor eu, gravida id, odio. Maecenas suscipit, risus et eleifend imperdiet, nisi orci ullamcorper massa, \net adipiscing orci velit quis magna.</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/cep00032.jpg\" alt=\"Sunburst Over River\" data-id=\"756\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/cep00032/\" class=\"wp-image-756\"/><figcaption>Sunburst over the Clinch River, \nSouthwest Virginia.</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/dsc02085.jpg\" alt=\"Orange Iris\" data-id=\"763\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dsc02085/\" class=\"wp-image-763\"/><figcaption>Orange Iris</figcaption>\n</figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/dcp_2082.jpg\" alt=\"Boardwalk\" data-id=\"757\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dcp_2082/\" class=\"wp-image-757\"/>\n<figcaption>Boardwalk at Westport, WA</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/100_5478.jpg\" alt=\"Bell on Wharf\" data-id=\"754\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/100_5478/\" class=\"wp-image-754\"/><figcaption>Bell on wharf in San \nFrancisco</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0767.jpg\" alt=\"Huatulco Coastline\" data-id=\"770\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery//img_0767/\" class=\"wp-image-770\"/>\n<figcaption>Coastline in Huatulco, Oaxaca, Mexico</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"columns\":2,\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery alignleft columns-2 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/spectacles.gif\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1692\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/about/clearing-floats/spectacles-2/\" class=\"wp-image-1692\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/unicorn-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Unicorn Wallpaper\" data-id=\"1045\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/08/08/post-format-image/unicorn-wallpaper/\" class=\"wp-image-1045\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/manhattansummer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"827\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/about/clearing-floats/olympus-digital-camera/\" class=\"wp-image-827\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/dsc20040724_152504_532.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"807\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dsc20040724_152504_532-2/\" class=\"wp-image-807\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><img src=\"http://wpthemetestdata.files.wordpress.com/2008/06/img_8399.jpg\" alt=\"Boat Barco Texture\" data-id=\"771\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/img_8399/\" class=\"wp-image-771\"/><figcaption>Boat BW PB Barco Texture Beautiful Fishing</figcaption>\n</figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some more text for taking up space.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A two column gallery, aligned to the left.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the editor, the image captions can be edited directly by clicking on the text.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the number of images cannot be divided into the number of columns you have selected, the default is to have the last image(s) automatically stretch to the width of your gallery.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":76} -->\n<div style=\"height:76px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A four column gallery with a wide width:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"columns\":4,\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery alignwide columns-4 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/dsc20050604_133440_34211.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1687\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dsc20050604_133440_3421/\" class=\"wp-image-1687\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/dsc20050315_145007_132.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1691\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dsc20050315_145007_132-2/\" class=\"wp-image-1691\"/></figure></li>\n<li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0513-1.jpg\" alt=\"Huatulco Coastline\" data-id=\"768\" \ndata-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/alas-i-have-found-my-shangri-la/\" class=\"wp-image-768\"/>\n<figcaption>Sunrise over the coast in Huatulco, Oaxaca, Mexico</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg\" alt=\"dsc20050813_115856_52\" data-id=\"617\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dsc20050813_115856_52/\" class=\"wp-image-617\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/dsc20050727_091048_222.jpg\" alt=\"dsc20050727_091048_222\" data-id=\"616\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/dsc20050727_091048_222/\" class=\"wp-image-616\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><img src=\"http://ztheme.loc/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/canola2.jpg\" alt=\"canola\" data-id=\"611\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/canola2/\" class=\"wp-image-611\"/><figcaption>\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Donec mollis. Quisque convallis libero in sapien pharetra tincidunt. Aliquam elit ante, malesuada id, \ntempor eu, gravida id, odio. Maecenas suscipit, risus et eleifend imperdiet, nisi orci ullamcorper massa, et adipiscing orci velit quis magna.</figcaption></figure>\n</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A five column gallery with normal  images:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"columns\":5,\"imageCrop\":false} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-5\"